      News.
     
      Art.
     
      Music industry.
     
      Books, magazines.
     
      Movie studios, Netflix, HBO, Disney.
     
      Video Games.
     
      Social media: Facebook, Medium, Tumblr, blogs.
  \textbf{Cultural products from \wordwikilink{http://pantheon.media.mit.edu/methods}{Pantheon}:}
      Writers, artists, movie directors, video game directors.
  
  
 
